  tutorialName: Combat_Targeting
  steps:
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    title: Targeting
    description: 'By clicking on the hero,allies or enemies all activated effects
      will target that entity. Depending on the effect of the card, different targets
      are enabled. For example a <<Shield 5 to an ally>> the enabled targets will
      be the hero and allies but if a card <<Deal 5 to an enemy>> then the targets
      will be the enemies! '
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    title: Target Indicator
    description: This is the targeting indicator to show what targets can be clicked!
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    title: Cancelling
    description: By pressing Right Click the card targeting will get cancelled!
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    title: Pattern Targeting
    description: 'Some Cards have special pattern targeting. These cards will hit
      all the targets depending on the card pattern. The first box indicates the
      target and then the pattern on how it. The target indicators will be displayed
      depending on the target you hover over. '
